high_descs: Turn around and head towards the front of the sink cabinet.
Pick up the hollow bronze tube on top of the sink cabinet.
Turn around and head towards the tall white cabinet on the left.
Open the bottom drawer of the tall white cabinet and place the tube in it.
Turn around and head towards the toilet on the right.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper sitting on top of the toilet.
Turn around and head back towards the tall white cabinet on the left.
Place the toilet paper in the bottom drawer next to the tube, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place two items in a drawer cabinet.

high_descs: turn around, face orange cup in between the sinks
pick up orange cup from counter
turn around, go to white dresser to the left
open bottom drawer of white dresser, place orange cup on right side of drawer, close drawer
turn around, go to red bin to the left of sinks
pick up toilet paper from right side of toilet tank
turn around, go to white dresser to the left
open bottom drawer of white dresser, place toilet paper to the left of orange cup in drawer, close drawer
anns.task_desc: Place orange cup and toilet paper roll in bottom drawer of white dresser

high_descs: Turn to the sinks behind you.
Grab the roll on the counter between the sinks.
Carrying the roll, turn around and walk to the cabinet to your left.
Open the lower drawer and place the roll inside drawer.
Turn around and walk to the toilet to your right.
Grab the roll of toilet paper on the toilet.
Carrying the roll of toilet paper, turn around and walk to the cabinet to your left.
Place the roll of toilet paper in the lower drawer next to the empty roll.
anns.task_desc: Place an empty roll and a roll of toilet paper in a cabinet.
